dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Tyler Simmons. May I have your name, please?
Hi, my name is Mary Smith.
Nice to meet you, Mary. Could you please provide me with your policy number for verification purposes?
Yes, my policy number is zero zero one two three four five.
Thank you, Mary. Lastly, could you confirm the make and model of your vehicle that this policy is associated with?
Great, thank you for the information, Mary. I'll proceed with verifying your policy details now.
Is there anything specific you would like to discuss or inquire about regarding your policy or coverage today?
I have a question about adding an additional driver to my policy.
Of course, I can assist you with that, Mary. Thank you for sharing your concerns.
Thank you for your time, Mary. If you have any further questions, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
